  introDialougeLines:
  - Uhhhhhhhhhh............................ hi............................
  - I......... don't......... talk to people much............................
  - You......... know Lilith too.........?
  - She's always been......... a colourful character.........
  - I think......... she might like some things here.........
  - There must be.... a bookshelf, a table and a mushroom lamp... somewhere...
