  - I think......... she might like some things here.........
  - There must be.... a bookshelf, a table and a mushroom lamp... somewhere...
  closingDialougeLines:
  - Woaw......... I think......... Lilith would like those.........
  - now the bee can take you back.........
  goAwayDialouge:
  - the bee can take you back.........
